= Resist Fire/Resist Cold =
'''Sphere:''' Special  
'''Level:''' 2  
'''Range:''' 30 yds  
'''Components:''' V, S, M (cross or holy water)  
'''Duration:''' 1 turn  
'''Casting Time:''' 2 rounds  
'''Area of Effect:''' 1 creature or area  
'''Saving Throw:''' None  

== Description ==
Grants creature 50% resistance to normal fire/cold, +3 or +6 on saves, and 25% or 50% damage reduction to magical fire/cold.

== Special Notes ==
* Treated as a [[Prayer]] in this campaign.
* All casting times and durations are increased by an order of magnitude (round → turn, turn → hour, etc).
* Requires cross and/or holy water.
